text: The Rochester Lancers are a semi-professional soccer team based in Rochester, New York. Rochester Lancers may also refer to: *Rochester Lancers (1967–80); member of the American Soccer League from 1967 to 1969 and the North American Soccer League from 1970 to 1980 *Rochester Lancers (2011–15); member of Major Indoor Soccer League from 2011 to 2014 and the Major Arena Soccer League from 2014 to 2015
title: Rochester Lancers (disambiguation)
